WEBVTT

01:39.479 --> 01:43.220
[Road to Success]

01:44.590 --> 01:47.930
[Episode 30]

01:51.150 --> 01:51.950
Later,

01:52.150 --> 01:54.000
use this nail to pin the eel down.

01:54.000 --> 01:55.200
I'll handle the rest.

01:55.280 --> 01:56.280
This is...

01:56.310 --> 01:57.400
your...

01:57.400 --> 01:58.640
s-signature dish?

01:58.640 --> 01:59.430
Yeah,

01:59.430 --> 02:00.480
braised eel.

02:00.480 --> 02:01.310
Let me tell you,

02:01.310 --> 02:04.480
my wife and Wang Tian both love it.

02:04.480 --> 02:06.480
W-Wang Tian loves eel?

02:07.200 --> 02:09.130
You're not afraid of eels, are you?

02:09.750 --> 02:10.280
I'm telling you,

02:10.280 --> 02:12.000
Wang Tian hates cowardly men the most.

02:12.000 --> 02:13.000
I-I'm not!

02:13.000 --> 02:14.120
I never said I was afraid.

02:14.120 --> 02:15.030
I can do it.

02:19.070 --> 02:19.720
Hold it.

02:20.520 --> 02:21.490
Remember, nail the head.

02:21.490 --> 02:23.290
Be careful not to nail your hand.

02:45.840 --> 02:47.120
Auntie!

02:47.120 --> 02:48.030
You're back!

02:48.030 --> 02:48.910
Yu Bo, you came.

02:50.030 --> 02:52.240
Why are you covered in so much mud?

02:52.240 --> 02:54.560
My mom insisted on
checking out the construction site.

02:54.560 --> 02:56.030
You're a civil engineering professor,

02:56.030 --> 02:57.030
not a contractor.

02:57.030 --> 02:58.450
Look at the mess on your clothes.

02:58.450 --> 03:00.370
A student of mine wanted me to
take a look at their project.

03:00.370 --> 03:01.400
Of course, I had to go, right?

03:01.400 --> 03:02.040
Yeah.

03:02.840 --> 03:04.030
Wang Tian, let me tell you...

03:04.030 --> 03:04.840
Well...

03:09.680 --> 03:10.630
What's wrong?

03:10.630 --> 03:11.490
Why are you gagging?

03:11.490 --> 03:12.620
Am I making you sick?

03:13.750 --> 03:14.560
No, I...

03:15.280 --> 03:16.440
It's just a reflex.

03:16.680 --> 03:18.280
A reflex?

03:19.120 --> 03:20.030
Excuse me.

03:20.030 --> 03:20.680
You guys clean up first.

03:20.680 --> 03:22.560
I n-need to go to the bathroom.

03:22.560 --> 03:23.790
Is he okay?

03:24.040 --> 03:24.880
Mom,

03:24.960 --> 03:25.840
are you okay?

03:27.910 --> 03:30.040
-Hello, Professor Kang.
-And this is?

03:30.490 --> 03:32.400
This is Ms. Lin Wanxing,

03:32.430 --> 03:33.480
a fellow teacher

03:33.520 --> 03:34.910
and my girlfriend.

03:36.220 --> 03:37.960
Hello, Ms. Lin.

03:37.960 --> 03:38.960
Nice to meet you.

03:38.960 --> 03:40.400
Kang Qiao.

03:40.400 --> 03:41.560
You're back.

03:43.030 --> 03:44.400
W-What happened?

03:47.750 --> 03:49.680
Nothing. I'm just happy to be home.

03:50.790 --> 03:51.430
Ms. Lin,

03:51.430 --> 03:52.870
I-I'll go wash up.

03:52.870 --> 03:54.280
I'm a mess.

03:54.910 --> 03:56.370
You guys keep her company.

03:58.120 --> 03:59.430
You invited Ms. Lin over

03:59.430 --> 04:00.840
without telling Mom beforehand?

04:00.840 --> 04:03.520
And Ms. Lin just happened to catch
Mom looking so disheveled.

04:03.520 --> 04:04.560
Wang,

04:04.560 --> 04:05.840
you're dead.

04:10.280 --> 04:10.680
Wait.

04:10.680 --> 04:11.560
I made eel.

04:13.560 --> 04:15.000
And braised!

04:15.590 --> 04:17.120
Let's all raise a glass to welcome

04:17.120 --> 04:17.800
Ms. Lin Wanxing.

04:17.800 --> 04:18.160
Thank you.

04:18.160 --> 04:18.779
Welcome, welcome.

04:18.779 --> 04:19.790
Welcome, welcome.

04:19.790 --> 04:21.240
Welcome, welcome.

04:24.870 --> 04:25.500
Oh, right.

04:26.190 --> 04:27.720
This is your favorite,

04:27.720 --> 04:29.000
braised eel.

04:31.560 --> 04:32.110
If you don't like it,

04:32.110 --> 04:32.950
let's switch to another dish.

04:32.950 --> 04:33.390
Let's switch to another dish.

04:33.390 --> 04:34.190
This is the one you love.

04:34.190 --> 04:34.790
Thank you.

04:47.800 --> 04:48.460
This one...

04:49.280 --> 04:50.500
Let me do it. Let me.

04:55.030 --> 04:56.070
How about this?

04:56.070 --> 04:56.950
Well,

04:56.950 --> 04:58.560
tomorrow I'll come back and make you

04:58.560 --> 05:00.000
braised soft-shell turtle—

05:00.000 --> 05:00.910
freshly slaughtered.

05:00.910 --> 05:01.660
Yu.

05:01.680 --> 05:02.440
Yu can do it.

05:02.470 --> 05:03.120
He has great knife skills.

05:03.120 --> 05:04.430
No, no, r-really, I can't.

05:04.430 --> 05:05.600
My knife skills aren't good.

05:05.600 --> 05:06.390
Not good at all.

05:06.390 --> 05:09.430
This is Wanxing's first time
visiting our home.

05:09.430 --> 05:11.120
Why didn't you tell me beforehand?

05:11.120 --> 05:12.390
Why keep it from me?

05:13.070 --> 05:13.680
Well...

05:14.310 --> 05:15.110
It's just that

05:15.270 --> 05:18.120
you've been so busy lately with research,

05:18.120 --> 05:19.160
writing papers,

05:19.160 --> 05:20.840
and running around to construction sites.

05:20.840 --> 05:22.030
I didn't want you to wear yourself out.

05:22.030 --> 05:22.830
So,

05:22.860 --> 05:23.600
whatever I could handle myself,

05:23.600 --> 05:25.560
I just went ahead a-and did it.

05:27.800 --> 05:28.830
This whole table of dishes—

05:28.830 --> 05:30.390
it must have taken you all afternoon.

05:30.390 --> 05:31.790
Just about 4 or 5 hours.

05:31.810 --> 05:32.659
It was fine.

05:32.820 --> 05:33.650
Mom,

05:33.670 --> 05:35.470
for all the hard work
Dad put into this meal,

05:35.470 --> 05:36.730
forgive him this time.

05:37.909 --> 05:38.590
Dad,

05:38.610 --> 05:39.680
punish yourself with a drink,

05:39.680 --> 05:41.280
and this matter will be over.

05:41.720 --> 05:43.510
That's my boy.

05:45.170 --> 05:46.020
Your Majesty,

05:46.510 --> 05:47.750
I was wrong.

05:50.230 --> 05:51.390
Blessings to the Empress Dowager.

05:51.390 --> 05:52.270
At ease.

05:55.110 --> 05:55.870
Wanxing,

05:55.890 --> 05:56.720
try this dish.

05:56.720 --> 05:58.540
It's my husband's specialty.

05:58.560 --> 05:59.409
Give it a try.

05:59.720 --> 06:02.120
This is my signature dish, braised eel.

06:02.120 --> 06:02.870
It's a secret recipe.

06:02.870 --> 06:04.600
You can't get it anywhere else.

06:04.870 --> 06:05.830
Come on, try it.

06:05.830 --> 06:07.910
My wife and Tian both love it the most.

06:07.940 --> 06:09.510
Ms. Lin, I want some.

06:10.910 --> 06:13.040
You just can't help yourself, can you?

06:15.840 --> 06:17.920
These noodles look great.

06:17.920 --> 06:19.560
Let me try the broth first.

06:19.560 --> 06:21.240
The broth is
what makes the noodles, right?

06:21.240 --> 06:23.190
This is also Chairman Wang's specialty.

06:23.190 --> 06:23.800
Dad,

06:23.830 --> 06:26.160
the broth is made from eel bones, right?

06:26.160 --> 06:26.600
Right.

06:26.600 --> 06:28.400
You just love the flavor, right?

06:29.920 --> 06:31.360
Uncle and Auntie,

06:31.360 --> 06:33.040
let me propose a toast.

06:35.000 --> 06:36.460
I need to use the restroom.

06:39.430 --> 06:41.000
What a lightweight.

06:41.920 --> 06:42.600
Wanxing,

06:43.120 --> 06:44.000
a toast to you.

06:44.000 --> 06:45.040
What are you doing?

06:45.040 --> 06:47.040
Making her drink on her first visit?

06:47.720 --> 06:49.130
I'll finish mine, and you do as you like.

06:49.130 --> 06:50.430
-Okay?
-You're putting her on the spot.

06:50.430 --> 06:51.600
If she doesn't drink,
it's disrespectful to you, right?

06:51.600 --> 06:52.400
That's not it.

06:53.390 --> 06:54.770
In this house,

06:54.800 --> 06:56.580
whether you respect me or not
doesn't matter.

06:56.580 --> 06:58.450
But you must respect
the lady of the house,

06:58.450 --> 06:59.070
right?

06:59.070 --> 07:01.000
Blessings to the Empress Dowager.

07:02.360 --> 07:03.290
Come on, come on.

07:03.720 --> 07:04.350
Right,

07:04.380 --> 07:05.190
Wanxing,

07:05.240 --> 07:07.030
do you know

07:07.060 --> 07:09.080
why I felt an instant connection with you?

07:09.080 --> 07:10.080
That's because

07:10.160 --> 07:12.490
you're very much like our Professor Kang.

07:14.920 --> 07:17.270
I didn't study hard when I was a kid,

07:17.270 --> 07:18.360
so I'm not very educated.

07:18.360 --> 07:20.560
One year, when I was doing business
in Shenzhen,

07:20.560 --> 07:22.830
I had a client whose surname was Situ.

07:22.830 --> 07:23.720
I even

07:23.720 --> 07:25.240
tried to act clever and asked him,

07:25.240 --> 07:25.920
"Sir,

07:25.920 --> 07:28.160
is it that your father's surname is Si

07:28.160 --> 07:30.020
and your mother's surname is Tu?"

07:30.520 --> 07:31.830
That was so embarrassing.

07:31.830 --> 07:33.240
Things like that happened a lot.

07:33.240 --> 07:33.800
So

07:33.800 --> 07:35.360
I've always believed

07:35.360 --> 07:36.040
that every family

07:36.040 --> 07:38.730
needs an intelligent, well-educated woman—

07:38.750 --> 07:40.170
that's what makes a household prosper.

07:40.170 --> 07:41.170
Remember that.

07:41.190 --> 07:44.240
Back then, I basically wore
Professor Kang down with my persistence

07:44.240 --> 07:45.900
until she agreed to be with me.

07:47.680 --> 07:50.700
I heard you were once the top scorer
on the college entrance exam, right?

07:50.700 --> 07:51.830
What was your score?

07:52.360 --> 07:53.680
Seven hundred and six points.

07:53.680 --> 07:55.159
See? See?

07:55.630 --> 07:57.390
Compared to our Professor Kang,

07:57.390 --> 07:58.800
you're no couch.

07:59.240 --> 08:00.510
"No slouch."

08:00.510 --> 08:03.480
Right, it's "no slouch." No slouch.

08:04.800 --> 08:05.560
Anyway,

08:07.000 --> 08:08.830
thank you so much

08:09.510 --> 08:11.630
for choosing our Wang Fa.

08:13.630 --> 08:15.040
To be honest, I also think

08:15.040 --> 08:17.100
you two are a perfect match.

08:17.130 --> 08:18.210
He's not like

08:18.240 --> 08:19.870
those delusional guys out there who are

08:19.870 --> 08:21.070
always chasing someone
way out of their league.

08:21.070 --> 08:22.020
Right, daughter?

08:22.020 --> 08:22.820
Dad.

08:24.160 --> 08:25.390
Come on, eat up.

08:25.420 --> 08:26.680
Let's have a drink together.

08:26.680 --> 08:27.240
Come on, come on.

08:27.240 --> 08:28.600
Cheers, cheers.

08:28.600 --> 08:29.120
Cheers.

08:29.120 --> 08:30.130
Welcome, Wanxing.

08:30.130 --> 08:31.040
Welcome, Wanxing.

08:31.040 --> 08:32.720
Welcome, welcome.

08:33.659 --> 08:34.860
Don't drink too much.

08:34.870 --> 08:35.840
I'm just happy.

08:35.840 --> 08:36.549
Just a little bit.

08:36.549 --> 08:37.909
Just a little.

08:39.000 --> 08:39.909
Then eat more.

08:52.360 --> 08:53.910
That's amazing.

08:56.480 --> 08:57.270
Don't let me have all the fun.

08:57.270 --> 08:58.030
You young people,

08:58.030 --> 08:58.720
be more lively.

08:58.720 --> 08:59.720
Don't just sit there with your phones.

08:59.720 --> 09:00.550
Come here. Come on.

09:00.550 --> 09:01.840
-Okay, I'll play.
-Go.

09:01.840 --> 09:03.150
Let me play with you.

09:04.320 --> 09:05.720
Why do you have to be part of everything?

09:05.720 --> 09:06.880
I'm actually pretty good at this.

09:06.880 --> 09:07.690
Really.

09:08.840 --> 09:09.570
Is that so?

09:11.030 --> 09:12.600
I may be getting on in years,

09:12.600 --> 09:15.130
but I still have
a strong competitive streak.

09:25.910 --> 09:27.480
See? I knew you were no good.

09:27.480 --> 09:28.680
And you just had to...

09:29.720 --> 09:30.490
Wanxing,

09:30.600 --> 09:31.390
Wang Fa, come here.

09:31.390 --> 09:32.000
Wanxing, if you don't know how,

09:32.000 --> 09:32.720
let Wang Fa teach you.

09:32.720 --> 09:33.510
Come on, come on.

09:33.510 --> 09:35.120
She has zero athletic talent.

09:35.120 --> 09:35.910
I'll do it.

09:36.270 --> 09:38.240
Let me play some rounds with our chairman.

09:38.240 --> 09:39.380
Let Wanxing play.

09:39.410 --> 09:42.030
-Dad is on a completely different level.
-Let me get familiar with it first.

09:42.030 --> 09:44.540
He used to spear fish
on the production team back in the day.

09:44.540 --> 09:46.420
Come here and let the kids play.

09:46.600 --> 09:48.930
Well, some things are better left unsaid.

09:49.600 --> 09:51.030
Let me give it a try.

09:52.790 --> 09:53.360
How about

09:53.360 --> 09:54.240
we have a round?

09:56.720 --> 09:57.400
Sure.

09:57.620 --> 09:58.340
Okay.

09:58.390 --> 09:59.720
I think that's fine.

09:59.720 --> 10:01.270
He sucks at darts.

10:01.600 --> 10:02.240
Anyway, if you lose,

10:02.240 --> 10:04.040
you have to do whatever she says.

10:06.720 --> 10:07.600
I'll give you a head start.

10:07.600 --> 10:08.480
You go first.

10:10.670 --> 10:11.790
This is going to be good.

10:11.790 --> 10:13.720
Challenge accepted.

10:17.320 --> 10:20.390
-Clearly didn't inherit my genes.
-You really suck,

10:20.390 --> 10:21.320
little brother.

10:25.510 --> 10:27.600
Step aside.

10:27.600 --> 10:29.000
Come on, Wanxing!

10:35.840 --> 10:36.480
Not bad.

10:36.480 --> 10:38.860
See? I knew Wanxing was good.

10:39.050 --> 10:40.120
Okay, you lost.

10:40.120 --> 10:41.510
What do you want him to do?

10:41.510 --> 10:42.720
I have a suggestion.

10:43.120 --> 10:45.120
Have you seen the photos of him
in women's clothes?

10:45.120 --> 10:46.000
The one

10:46.000 --> 10:47.960
where he's wearing a qipao
with a flower crown?

10:47.960 --> 10:49.000
I just saw the photo upstairs.

10:49.000 --> 10:50.260
Isn't that hilarious?

10:50.600 --> 10:51.200
Okay.

10:51.360 --> 10:53.290
How about a qipao and flower crown?

10:53.510 --> 10:54.720
Are you asking for it?

10:54.720 --> 10:56.320
I think that's a great idea.

10:56.320 --> 10:57.240
Duly noted.

10:58.910 --> 10:59.960
That's so fun, honey.

10:59.960 --> 11:00.510
Come on, come on,

11:00.510 --> 11:01.000
honey,

11:01.000 --> 11:03.930
how about I take you along
to try the flower crown too?

11:10.600 --> 11:12.120
Come on, we're already here.

11:12.120 --> 11:14.320
Just play one round.

11:14.320 --> 11:15.120
No.

11:15.120 --> 11:16.230
I'm very busy.

11:17.000 --> 11:17.720
We have a guest,

11:17.720 --> 11:20.600
and you're just sitting here
glued to your phone.

11:23.120 --> 11:23.840
Fine.

11:23.840 --> 11:24.870
If I win,

11:24.870 --> 11:27.080
you're not allowed to hang around
my office for no reason anymore.

11:27.080 --> 11:28.550
And if I win,

11:28.550 --> 11:30.240
you have to agree to one request of mine.

11:30.240 --> 11:31.120
Deal.

11:33.240 --> 11:34.500
Give the darts to them.

11:35.440 --> 11:36.240
You got this.

11:39.120 --> 11:40.650
Yu Bo used to compete in

11:40.700 --> 11:42.600
professional dart tournaments
back in the UK.

11:42.600 --> 11:45.120
No wonder he's so confident.

11:48.120 --> 11:48.870
Nice!

11:49.440 --> 11:51.130
As expected of Kang Qiao's daughter.

11:51.130 --> 11:52.210
So amazing.

12:06.150 --> 12:06.600
Wait.

12:07.080 --> 12:08.030
Seriously?

12:08.600 --> 12:10.080
When Wanxing hit the board,

12:10.080 --> 12:10.840
you applauded so enthusiastically.

12:10.840 --> 12:13.000
How come it's so cold when it's my turn?

12:17.080 --> 12:18.240
Alright, go ahead.

12:18.240 --> 12:19.440
What's your request?

12:20.960 --> 12:22.630
My request is that...

12:26.440 --> 12:27.910
you really look at me.

12:28.840 --> 12:30.440
Look me in the eye, properly.

12:38.750 --> 12:39.510
I just did.

12:41.090 --> 12:44.750
You're even more ordinary
than this quarter's financial report.

12:47.600 --> 12:49.600
My sister's a master roaster.

12:50.600 --> 12:52.000
How am I a master roaster?

12:52.390 --> 12:53.360
Your words are savage,

12:53.360 --> 12:54.320
and your actions are even worse.

12:54.320 --> 12:57.550
-Let's all play. Let me show you.
-You started that flower crown thing.

12:57.550 --> 12:59.000
I still haven't settled that score
with you.

12:59.000 --> 13:00.000
You were smiling so happily in that photo

13:00.000 --> 13:01.330
from when you were a kid.

13:02.240 --> 13:02.840
I'll stick this dart in you.

13:02.840 --> 13:03.360
D-Don't...

13:03.360 --> 13:03.720
Dad,

13:03.720 --> 13:04.380
look at him.

13:04.670 --> 13:06.330
Let Dad show you how it's done.

13:06.600 --> 13:08.530
You can't lose to someone like him.

13:08.670 --> 13:09.360
Watch carefully.

13:09.360 --> 13:10.510
It's too rowdy in here.

13:10.510 --> 13:11.600
Want to go out for some fresh air?

13:11.600 --> 13:12.200
Standard posture.

13:12.200 --> 13:13.200
Watch carefully.

13:14.720 --> 13:18.120
-Dad, you're so good.
-Well, the old fox still has his tricks.

13:21.630 --> 13:23.000
Please excuse

13:23.790 --> 13:25.200
our family.

13:26.200 --> 13:28.240
My husband can be a bit much sometimes,

13:28.240 --> 13:29.360
like a big kid.

13:30.670 --> 13:31.200
No.

13:31.600 --> 13:33.110
He's very nice.

13:33.280 --> 13:34.670
You're all wonderful.

13:34.750 --> 13:36.410
I think you're wonderful too.

13:36.480 --> 13:38.720
The moment I saw you today, I thought,

13:39.080 --> 13:41.000
"I wish we'd met sooner."

13:42.960 --> 13:44.200
Have you...

13:45.700 --> 13:47.700
heard about my past?

13:48.600 --> 13:49.720
Does that matter?

13:57.080 --> 13:59.010
I like looking at the stars.

14:01.000 --> 14:02.000
Take the Andromeda Galaxy

14:02.000 --> 14:03.930
we're looking at now, for example.

14:04.120 --> 14:05.600
It's about

14:05.600 --> 14:07.480
2.54 million light-years away.

14:08.600 --> 14:10.930
It's about twice the size
of the Milky Way,

14:11.240 --> 14:13.510
with over a trillion stars.

14:14.120 --> 14:15.120
Yet to us,

14:15.140 --> 14:16.380
it's nothing more

14:16.630 --> 14:18.750
than a blurry patch of light.

14:20.000 --> 14:20.840
Its vastness,

14:20.840 --> 14:21.840
its profundity,

14:21.840 --> 14:23.510
its brilliance,

14:23.510 --> 14:24.840
its true form—

14:25.750 --> 14:26.720
most people

14:27.320 --> 14:28.840
never truly

14:28.840 --> 14:30.480
understand any of it.

14:32.630 --> 14:34.000
But so what?

14:34.990 --> 14:39.350
Humanity's limited perspective
and incomplete understanding

14:40.000 --> 14:41.810
don't change

14:41.830 --> 14:43.230
its objective existence

14:43.840 --> 14:45.440
or its timeless beauty.

14:48.540 --> 14:49.660
I understand now.

14:52.840 --> 14:54.480
Actually, since my husband

14:54.480 --> 14:56.200
likes you so much,

14:56.840 --> 14:59.390
he must have looked into your past.

14:59.480 --> 15:01.630
He's not as clueless as he seems.

15:03.400 --> 15:06.000
Of course, he's not exactly smart either.

15:06.530 --> 15:08.010
He went bankrupt twice.

15:08.030 --> 15:09.910
Good thing my income is stable.

15:09.940 --> 15:13.000
Otherwise, our whole family
would be out on the street.

15:15.360 --> 15:16.600
Actually...

15:18.480 --> 15:19.600
ever since

15:19.600 --> 15:21.480
Wang Fa's student

15:21.480 --> 15:22.960
had that accident,

15:24.320 --> 15:26.050
he's been carrying it with him.

15:27.360 --> 15:29.240
We tried everything we could

15:29.240 --> 15:30.400
to make him

15:30.510 --> 15:31.960
happy again.

15:33.600 --> 15:35.130
But nothing really worked.

15:37.240 --> 15:38.200
Today,

15:38.200 --> 15:39.330
seeing him laugh...

15:40.120 --> 15:41.850
laugh that wholeheartedly...

15:44.400 --> 15:46.590
made me so, so happy.

15:49.190 --> 15:50.110
I think

15:51.720 --> 15:53.920
you're the one who brought him out of it.

15:54.600 --> 15:55.870
For your sake, he's

15:55.870 --> 15:57.670
finally opened his heart again.

16:03.440 --> 16:04.200
Thank you.

16:22.000 --> 16:22.600
Son.

16:23.320 --> 16:24.480
Do you have to go back to Hongjing?

16:24.480 --> 16:26.630
The guest rooms are all empty.

16:27.240 --> 16:28.720
I can stay!

16:28.720 --> 16:30.840
Which room will I be staying in?

16:30.840 --> 16:32.470
Are you...

16:32.470 --> 16:34.000
I'm talking to my son.

16:34.000 --> 16:36.000
Why are you moving around so much?

16:36.000 --> 16:36.750
No,

16:36.750 --> 16:38.720
Uncle, listen to me!

16:38.740 --> 16:44.100
I'm only 3 months and 4 days older
than Wang Tian.

16:44.510 --> 16:45.960
Tian, tell him

16:45.960 --> 16:47.150
I'm only that much older than you.

16:47.150 --> 16:48.240
Okay. Yes, yes.

16:48.480 --> 16:50.360
Quick, have the driver
take this drunk home.

16:50.360 --> 16:51.750
No! I...

16:51.750 --> 16:55.000
I want Fa to take me back.

16:55.480 --> 16:57.120
-Okay, I'll take you.
-What a lightweight.

16:57.120 --> 16:59.000
You're my former manager after all.

16:59.000 --> 17:01.600
Uncle, Auntie, thank you for today.

17:01.600 --> 17:02.600
Come by often from now on.

17:02.600 --> 17:03.570
Come by often.

17:03.840 --> 17:05.069
We're really glad you came.

17:05.069 --> 17:05.930
We're leaving.

17:05.960 --> 17:07.960
Drive safely on the road.

17:07.960 --> 17:09.589
We will.

17:10.310 --> 17:11.480
Such a lightweight.

17:12.400 --> 17:13.270
So weak.

17:24.030 --> 17:25.560
What are you smiling about?

17:27.450 --> 17:29.240
I just think

17:29.830 --> 17:31.750
your family is really lovable.

17:32.720 --> 17:33.960
I'm so jealous.

17:38.830 --> 17:39.630
From now on...

17:41.510 --> 17:43.040
they'll be your family too.

18:03.350 --> 18:05.810
Is this how you treat
your comrade-in-arms?

18:06.510 --> 18:08.440
Who said I'm his comrade-in-arms?

18:09.510 --> 18:10.480
Then,

18:11.000 --> 18:13.200
what are we going to do with him tonight?

18:13.240 --> 18:14.700
Let him stay at your place?

18:16.230 --> 18:17.070
Okay.

18:18.590 --> 18:19.720
That obedient?

18:20.720 --> 18:22.110
My family tradition:

18:22.590 --> 18:24.920
the lady of the house makes the decisions.

19:11.840 --> 19:14.100
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

19:14.800 --> 19:18.920
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

19:19.420 --> 19:21.380
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

19:25.590 --> 19:27.240
Just kiss her if you want to.

19:27.240 --> 19:29.350
Why are you dragging it out?

19:35.720 --> 19:36.680
Let's go home.

19:37.640 --> 19:39.440
Go home.

19:48.720 --> 19:49.310
Do you know

19:49.310 --> 19:52.640
he was trying to
sneak a kiss from you just now?

19:56.480 --> 19:57.440
Ms. Lin.

19:59.240 --> 20:00.720
Tell me honestly.

20:02.270 --> 20:03.880
Am I really that ordinary?

20:04.550 --> 20:05.270
Not at all.

20:05.270 --> 20:07.000
I think you're very special.

20:07.000 --> 20:09.550
Right? Aren't I?

20:09.550 --> 20:11.880
Aren't I?

20:12.720 --> 20:13.720
Let me tell you,

20:14.380 --> 20:17.640
my handsomeness has layers.

20:18.000 --> 20:22.030
But Tian just can't appreciate it.

20:22.920 --> 20:23.920
I'm warning you,

20:24.640 --> 20:26.030
if you can't keep your hands to yourself,

20:26.030 --> 20:28.560
I'll dump you by the roadside
to feed the dogs.

20:30.070 --> 20:30.680
Doggie.

20:31.110 --> 20:31.640
Doggie.

20:32.070 --> 20:33.200
Where's the doggie?

20:33.440 --> 20:34.840
The doggie's over there.

20:34.880 --> 20:37.200
The doggie's over there.

20:45.680 --> 20:48.280
You were trying to
sneak a kiss from me just now?

20:53.240 --> 20:54.920
If I were a doggie,

20:54.920 --> 20:57.520
I'd want to be
a Cavalier King Charles Spaniel.

20:58.680 --> 21:00.590
You'd better not be a dog.

21:01.790 --> 21:04.250
Cavalier King Charles Spaniels
are so cute.

21:06.480 --> 21:08.010
Wrong way.

21:10.480 --> 21:12.160
Rest early. Good night.

21:12.160 --> 21:12.880
Good night.

21:13.720 --> 21:14.850
Thank you for today.

21:15.000 --> 21:15.920
Good night.

21:15.920 --> 21:17.920
Thank you for everything today too.

21:21.590 --> 21:24.550
I could also be a Golden Retriever.

21:32.910 --> 21:33.560
[Wang Fa]

21:38.160 --> 21:38.920
Hello?

21:39.690 --> 21:41.170
Ms. Lin,

21:41.200 --> 21:42.790
Wang Fa lost to you!

21:42.790 --> 21:46.480
When are you making him
wear a flower crown?

21:47.790 --> 21:50.120
Can you just sleep quietly, you drunkard?

21:50.310 --> 21:51.160
Hello.

21:51.160 --> 21:52.440
Don't listen to him.

21:52.440 --> 21:53.240
Okay.

21:53.240 --> 21:54.000
Noted.

21:55.880 --> 21:57.000
Okay...

21:57.000 --> 21:58.000
Okay to what?

21:58.000 --> 22:00.460
To take you
to try on a flower crown tomorrow.

22:02.160 --> 22:04.480
A bet's a bet, Mr. Win.

22:06.720 --> 22:07.480
Fine.

22:08.400 --> 22:09.310
Rest early.

22:09.920 --> 22:10.550
You too.

22:21.160 --> 22:23.000
Ivory,

22:23.830 --> 22:25.720
a bet's a bet.

22:28.880 --> 22:29.830
What do you think of me in this outfit?

22:29.830 --> 22:30.790
Fix your hair.

22:30.790 --> 22:31.750
-It looks good.
-It really suits you.

22:31.750 --> 22:32.350
Excuse me.

22:32.350 --> 22:33.880
Come, stand a little further forward.

22:33.880 --> 22:34.960
Look here.

22:38.480 --> 22:39.480
Sorry.

22:42.960 --> 22:44.880
I think I'm a bit too rough-looking

22:44.880 --> 22:46.550
and too tan for the flower crown look.

22:46.550 --> 22:47.510
Relax.

22:47.510 --> 22:49.350
Places like this usually do
pretty heavy makeup.

22:49.350 --> 22:50.310
They'll make you nice and fair.

22:50.310 --> 22:51.160
Let's go.

22:52.350 --> 22:53.400
Okay, one more.

22:53.400 --> 22:54.070
Look.

22:53.600 --> 22:57.570
[No More Anxiety]

22:54.070 --> 22:55.270
Do you like this look?

22:55.960 --> 22:56.880
So pretty.

22:57.370 --> 22:58.850
So beautiful.

22:58.880 --> 23:01.010
Here, and there's more in the back too.

23:02.960 --> 23:04.240
I like this one as well.

23:04.240 --> 23:04.880
Yeah.

23:04.960 --> 23:06.240
We should take photos
in a few more outfits.

23:06.240 --> 23:07.880
Okay. Do you have sample pictures?

23:07.880 --> 23:08.790
Could you recommend a few?

23:08.790 --> 23:09.510
Yes, yes.

23:11.270 --> 23:12.330
This one's lovely.

23:13.440 --> 23:14.310
Come on.

23:30.440 --> 23:31.840
Does this look good on me?

23:32.000 --> 23:32.680
Yes.

23:33.400 --> 23:34.680
Let me take a picture of you.

23:34.680 --> 23:38.650
[No More Anxiety]

23:43.240 --> 23:43.880
Alright.

23:43.880 --> 23:44.240
Okay.

23:44.240 --> 23:45.030
Your turn.

23:48.400 --> 23:49.720
Hey, you two,

23:49.720 --> 23:50.790
would you like flower crowns?

23:50.790 --> 23:52.750
Ma'am, my boyfriend wants it.

23:52.750 --> 23:53.720
Sure.

23:53.720 --> 23:55.960
My hair's too short
to pin anything into, right?

23:55.960 --> 23:57.880
Even bald people can wear flower crowns.

23:57.880 --> 23:58.880
Hear that?

23:58.880 --> 24:00.610
Even bald people can wear them.

24:02.440 --> 24:04.400
A bet is a bet.

24:04.400 --> 24:05.930
I'll go pick a color for you.

24:07.400 --> 24:08.480
Yellow, maybe.

24:08.960 --> 24:10.020
It's more elegant.

24:15.270 --> 24:17.480
It was clearly a pink one in the photo,

24:17.480 --> 24:19.030
bright pink.

24:20.240 --> 24:21.790
It suits you perfectly.

24:27.240 --> 24:28.000
Let me think—

24:28.000 --> 24:30.640
we're still missing a women's qipao.

24:30.640 --> 24:31.160
Well,

24:31.160 --> 24:33.420
do we really have to recreate it exactly?

24:37.480 --> 24:39.270
Ms. Lin,

24:39.270 --> 24:40.720
please,

24:40.720 --> 24:42.920
let me off this time.

24:44.270 --> 24:45.030
Alright then.

24:45.030 --> 24:46.920
But since we're here,

24:46.920 --> 24:48.720
I'll wear a flower crown myself.

24:50.310 --> 24:51.480
I think

24:51.480 --> 24:52.880
it's you who wanted to wear one

24:52.880 --> 24:54.280
from the very beginning.

24:55.480 --> 24:56.510
That's right.

24:56.510 --> 24:58.200
The moment I saw your photo,

24:58.200 --> 24:59.860
my heart was already set on it.

25:01.880 --> 25:03.510
Ma'am, could you pick a color for me?

25:03.510 --> 25:04.510
Alright.

25:04.930 --> 25:07.480
After you're done,
you can go take pictures by the seaside.

25:07.480 --> 25:08.240
It'll look so pretty.

25:08.240 --> 25:08.920
The seaside?

25:08.920 --> 25:09.480
The seaside.

25:09.480 --> 25:10.000
Yeah.

25:10.550 --> 25:12.440
The beach around here is quite beautiful.

25:12.440 --> 25:14.170
Photos look even better there.

25:44.510 --> 25:45.070
Look.

25:45.920 --> 25:47.920
There's a message in a bottle over there.

25:47.920 --> 25:49.050
What a coincidence.

25:56.000 --> 25:58.720
It really is... quite a coincidence.

26:00.310 --> 26:01.510
Why don't you open it?

26:02.870 --> 26:04.150
Don't tell me

26:04.480 --> 26:06.880
there's an engagement ring hidden inside.

26:07.510 --> 26:08.400
No ring.

26:20.070 --> 26:21.530
It's an application form.

26:21.780 --> 26:23.520
[Yongchuan University
PhD Program Application Form]

26:27.990 --> 26:29.650
♪ Two souls aligned ♪

26:28.790 --> 26:31.750
When I accompanied you back to
Yongchuan University last time,

26:31.750 --> 26:32.830
Director Jia asked

26:31.860 --> 26:33.620
♪ In silent gravity ♪

26:33.440 --> 26:35.840
if you wanted to
go back and finish your PhD.

26:36.020 --> 26:37.820
♪ Heal my heart ♪

26:36.880 --> 26:38.780
From the look in your eyes at that time,

26:38.780 --> 26:41.200
♪ With every part of you ♪

26:38.830 --> 26:39.960
I could tell you did.

26:43.950 --> 26:45.520
♪ Our words flow ♪

26:44.110 --> 26:45.440
I'm sure I wasn't wrong.

26:47.420 --> 26:49.320
♪ A gentle stream ♪

26:48.160 --> 26:49.960
So this whole elaborate plan...

26:50.670 --> 26:52.160
was all for this?

26:51.730 --> 26:53.780
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

26:53.700 --> 26:55.240
After we finish the last match,

26:54.560 --> 26:56.570
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

26:55.790 --> 26:58.270
the kids will have to prepare for
the college entrance exam.

26:58.270 --> 26:59.620
I think after that,

26:59.310 --> 27:04.770
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

27:00.270 --> 27:02.200
you should start a new chapter too.

27:06.160 --> 27:07.640
When did you prepare this?

27:07.120 --> 27:08.550
♪ We trace the roads ♪

27:07.640 --> 27:08.770
Early this morning.

27:08.920 --> 27:09.830
I forced Yu Bo to come and do it.

27:09.520 --> 27:12.470
♪ That never see an end ♪

27:10.520 --> 27:14.120
I couldn't let him put me through
all that last night for nothing.

27:15.310 --> 27:18.200
♪ We softly calm the hidden doubt ♪

27:16.680 --> 27:18.380
More than being my wife,

27:19.480 --> 27:20.480
I want you...

27:19.510 --> 27:23.890
♪ Seen in each other's eyes ♪

27:22.030 --> 27:24.630
to be the radiant, shining
Lin Wanxing you are.

27:24.780 --> 27:28.630
♪ And wake the warmth inside ♪

27:30.700 --> 27:32.950
♪ Life begins alone ♪

27:33.810 --> 27:36.220
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

27:38.620 --> 27:40.630
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

27:41.440 --> 27:44.740
♪ To light our way back home ♪

27:46.800 --> 27:48.710
♪ True love is not just ♪

27:49.300 --> 27:50.900
♪ The gaze when two hearts first meet ♪

27:51.810 --> 27:56.560
♪ It's courage in the arms ♪

27:53.110 --> 27:55.310
Are you still going to take photos of me?

27:56.440 --> 27:57.570
I'll do it right now.

27:58.620 --> 28:00.700
♪ We stand as one ♪

28:02.480 --> 28:04.140
♪ Our words flow ♪

28:04.150 --> 28:08.470
[Yongchuan University
PhD Program Application Form]

28:05.950 --> 28:07.850
♪ A gentle stream ♪

28:10.260 --> 28:12.310
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

28:13.090 --> 28:15.090
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

28:17.840 --> 28:22.800
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

28:22.200 --> 28:23.600
What should we eat later?

28:26.000 --> 28:26.510
Boss,

28:26.510 --> 28:27.240
Wen Chengye.

28:29.330 --> 28:30.460
-Wen!
-Wen Chengye!

28:32.200 --> 28:33.030
Wen Chengye,

28:33.030 --> 28:35.030
don't forget the team meeting
this afternoon.

28:35.030 --> 28:37.490
-Got it.
-It's about us reaching the finals!

28:38.240 --> 28:39.070
Did you hear that?

28:39.070 --> 28:40.310
We made it to the finals!

28:40.310 --> 28:41.310
Got it!

28:41.640 --> 28:42.680
Qin Ao is so handsome.

28:42.680 --> 28:44.140
They made it to the finals.

28:44.270 --> 28:45.680
Qin Ao is so cool!

28:45.680 --> 28:47.750
Qin Ao, you're so cool!

28:47.750 --> 28:49.310
Let's go watch it together!

28:50.750 --> 28:51.950
So cool!

28:52.070 --> 28:54.720
Go for it!

29:11.790 --> 29:13.070
Look what this is.

29:13.070 --> 29:14.480
Everyone!

29:14.750 --> 29:15.830
Hello, Director.

29:15.850 --> 29:18.110
-Take a look at these.
-Hello, Director.

29:19.640 --> 29:20.480
I heard from Ms. Lin

29:20.480 --> 29:22.960
that you guys like
this place's milk tea the best.

29:22.960 --> 29:24.240
Today, I, Qian,

29:24.240 --> 29:25.960
paid out of my own pocket

29:25.960 --> 29:27.550
to reward all our warriors!

29:28.200 --> 29:29.550
Good job, everyone!

29:30.790 --> 29:31.870
Thank you, Director!

29:31.870 --> 29:33.830
-Let me have one.
-Which one?

29:37.000 --> 29:37.960
Director,

29:37.960 --> 29:40.090
you're being awfully generous today.

29:40.400 --> 29:41.790
Was I really that stingy before?

29:41.790 --> 29:42.720
Of course.

29:42.720 --> 29:44.160
Isn't this the first time
you've ever bought us anything?

29:44.160 --> 29:44.880
Alright.

29:45.200 --> 29:46.530
I'll buy more next time!

29:50.640 --> 29:51.480
Students...

29:51.920 --> 29:52.570
Director Qian,

29:52.570 --> 29:54.960
you might as well just
call us "little brats" like before.

29:54.960 --> 29:56.360
It's more affectionate.

29:57.270 --> 29:58.000
Alright,

29:58.400 --> 29:59.960
little brats!

30:03.240 --> 30:05.070
I'm really happy today.

30:06.680 --> 30:08.340
Seeing how far you've all come

30:08.880 --> 30:10.640
makes every bit of it worthwhile—

30:10.640 --> 30:12.200
all those hours I spent

30:12.200 --> 30:15.600
wearing my reading glasses,
helping you fill your composition grids

30:15.600 --> 30:18.930
one square at a time,
and copying English poems line by line.

30:21.000 --> 30:22.060
It was all worth it.

30:23.400 --> 30:24.000
Alright.

30:24.510 --> 30:26.140
I'm here today

30:26.170 --> 30:27.570
representing the school

30:27.880 --> 30:29.160
to talk to you all about

30:29.640 --> 30:31.720
the special admission policy.

30:37.240 --> 30:38.840
I think they had it last year.

30:40.620 --> 30:41.750
Special admission.

30:43.000 --> 30:44.200
What exactly is it?

30:44.550 --> 30:45.960
Well, the football game

30:46.480 --> 30:47.680
is about to start,

30:47.680 --> 30:49.000
and it's the finals.

30:49.880 --> 30:51.510
If you win

30:51.510 --> 30:53.240
the championship,

30:53.750 --> 30:56.200
3 players among you

30:56.200 --> 31:00.480
may qualify
for special university admission.

31:01.720 --> 31:03.850
That's what special admission means.

31:05.640 --> 31:06.750
Director,

31:06.770 --> 31:09.350
how many points can it lower
the admission threshold by?

31:09.350 --> 31:10.280
I looked into it.

31:10.400 --> 31:12.330
Based on your current grades,

31:12.440 --> 31:14.440
if you guys push a little harder,

31:14.440 --> 31:16.220
you should be able to reach

31:16.010 --> 31:17.760
[Special Admission]

31:16.720 --> 31:19.320
the score requirement
for special admission.

31:20.640 --> 31:22.160
Does it only apply
if we win the championship?

31:22.160 --> 31:23.960
Well, of course, the runner-up works too.

31:23.960 --> 31:25.160
It's just that there won't be

31:25.160 --> 31:26.000
those 3

31:26.000 --> 31:27.640
fixed special admission slots.

31:27.640 --> 31:30.500
So obviously,
winning the championship is better.

31:31.480 --> 31:32.440
Really,

31:32.470 --> 31:35.680
the school hopes you can
achieve good results.

31:36.150 --> 31:39.250
[Special Admission]

31:36.380 --> 31:37.650
But...

31:39.160 --> 31:40.200
I'd

31:40.640 --> 31:42.030
also like to say

31:42.370 --> 31:44.210
a few words from the heart.

31:48.940 --> 31:50.670
I still remember two years ago,

31:50.920 --> 31:53.680
when you first came to this school.

31:54.240 --> 31:56.070
You were even rowdier back then.

31:56.720 --> 31:57.480
But

31:57.790 --> 32:00.480
your eyes were shining with light.

32:01.240 --> 32:02.440
I thought to myself then

32:02.440 --> 32:05.720
that you were a bunch of good boys
with ambition.

32:07.880 --> 32:09.680
But not long after,

32:09.680 --> 32:11.200
your class fell apart,

32:11.200 --> 32:13.200
and so did your spirits.

32:13.200 --> 32:14.270
Especially

32:14.550 --> 32:16.920
that light in your eyes—

32:17.610 --> 32:19.550
I could no longer see it.

32:20.440 --> 32:21.720
It worried me deeply.

32:22.510 --> 32:24.710
I really wanted to do something for you,

32:25.120 --> 32:26.030
but

32:26.680 --> 32:29.310
there was only so much I could do.

32:30.000 --> 32:31.160
Later,

32:31.160 --> 32:32.920
Mr. Lin found me

32:33.240 --> 32:35.160
and asked me to be this "mystery person"

32:35.160 --> 32:37.680
to carry out this secret plan.

32:38.000 --> 32:39.240
I was very happy.

32:39.920 --> 32:40.980
I agreed on the spot

32:40.980 --> 32:42.780
without a moment's hesitation.

32:44.920 --> 32:46.200
I have always believed

32:47.000 --> 32:49.200
that as an educator,

32:49.680 --> 32:52.000
we must never let

32:52.000 --> 32:54.720
the fire in the students' hearts go out.

33:00.140 --> 33:01.870
And now, I'm truly happy

33:02.070 --> 33:02.680
to see

33:02.680 --> 33:05.540
that fire burning bright
in your hearts once again.

33:06.960 --> 33:07.550
Really.

33:08.350 --> 33:10.270
No matter whether you win

33:10.270 --> 33:12.200
the championship this time or not,

33:12.880 --> 33:14.200
in my heart,

33:15.750 --> 33:16.960
you are all the best.

33:18.960 --> 33:20.440
I can proudly say

33:21.200 --> 33:22.070
that I

33:22.070 --> 33:27.070
am a teacher of Hongjing No. 8 High School's
star football team.

33:27.720 --> 33:29.400
Our football players

33:30.960 --> 33:32.310
are the best.

33:33.400 --> 33:34.460
The absolute best.

33:45.400 --> 33:46.200
Qian,

33:47.400 --> 33:50.000
the other day, Chen Jianghe and I
snuck off with your bike

33:50.000 --> 33:51.400
and ended up breaking it.

33:51.550 --> 33:54.350
Now it makes a rattling noise
whenever you ride it.

33:55.240 --> 33:55.970
Don't worry.

33:56.640 --> 33:58.370
I'll definitely fix it for you.

33:59.510 --> 34:00.030
Good.

34:00.750 --> 34:01.960
Since you're being real with me,

34:01.960 --> 34:03.690
I've got to be real with you too.

34:03.920 --> 34:06.270
I wasn't going to tell you at first,

34:06.270 --> 34:07.070
but now

34:07.070 --> 34:09.670
I'll share another
piece of good news with you.

34:09.880 --> 34:11.150
In order to

34:11.150 --> 34:15.150
let you focus wholeheartedly on
preparing for the finals,

34:15.150 --> 34:16.730
starting next week,

34:16.920 --> 34:19.790
the school is giving you 2 weeks off

34:20.230 --> 34:22.230
for intensive training!

34:23.120 --> 34:24.280
Two weeks?

34:26.030 --> 34:27.840
Thank you, Director!

34:28.880 --> 34:30.670
Thank you, Director!

34:31.920 --> 34:32.710
Alright, alright!

34:32.710 --> 34:34.480
M-M-My job here is done.

34:34.480 --> 34:35.190
You guys, enjoy the milk tea.

34:35.190 --> 34:36.150
-Enjoy the milk tea.
-Okay, okay.

34:36.150 --> 34:37.710
Bye-bye! Bye-bye!

34:38.710 --> 34:39.920
See you tomorrow!

34:40.630 --> 34:41.920
That's great!

34:43.000 --> 34:43.880
Fight on, guys!

34:43.880 --> 34:45.320
-Fight on!
-Yeah!

34:49.360 --> 34:50.400
Just got the news—

34:50.920 --> 34:53.280
Hengjiu defeated
their opponent 7-0 with ease

34:53.280 --> 34:54.710
and advanced to
the Youth Super League finals.

34:54.710 --> 34:56.710
We fought tooth and nail to advance,

34:56.800 --> 34:58.400
while they cruised through.

34:58.630 --> 35:00.630
That final boss really is a final boss,

35:00.630 --> 35:02.360
scoring like that in the semifinals.

35:02.360 --> 35:03.510
They're just

35:03.510 --> 35:04.840
in a league of their own.

35:04.840 --> 35:06.570
When we face them in the finals,

35:06.800 --> 35:08.440
it'll be like two bitter rivals

35:08.440 --> 35:09.640
going head-to-head.

35:13.480 --> 35:14.290
Starting tomorrow,

35:13.660 --> 35:16.230
[Little Savage Tribe]

35:14.320 --> 35:15.710
we'll focus on analyzing
Hengjiu's playing style and discuss

35:15.710 --> 35:18.670
-targeted tactics for the finals.
-Coach has new strategies.

35:18.670 --> 35:19.760
But

35:19.760 --> 35:21.480
no matter how good the tactics are,

35:21.480 --> 35:23.340
can we really beat the final boss?

35:23.550 --> 35:25.710
After all, in our last match against them,

35:25.710 --> 35:27.510
they scored 11 goals against us.

35:37.280 --> 35:38.440
You can still eat?

35:39.070 --> 35:40.230
Why wouldn't I?

35:40.920 --> 35:42.400
Is being this dejected

35:42.400 --> 35:44.130
going to help you win the match?

35:48.230 --> 35:49.030
Well said.

35:49.630 --> 35:50.840
Eat as much as we can now,

35:50.840 --> 35:53.320
and give it everything
we've got on the field later.

35:53.320 --> 35:54.030
Not eating?

35:54.280 --> 35:55.210
I'm eating then.

35:57.030 --> 35:58.230
Come on, eat up.

35:59.510 --> 36:01.840
I think we should stop being intimidated.

36:01.920 --> 36:03.280
Who cares if they're the final boss?

36:03.280 --> 36:05.630
At least we have a chance
to compete against them.

36:05.630 --> 36:06.880
Cheer up, guys.

36:07.230 --> 36:08.160
Just do our best.

36:08.230 --> 36:09.070
-Come on, guys.
-Yeah.

36:09.070 --> 36:10.190
Cheer up, guys.

36:11.230 --> 36:12.000
That's right.

36:12.000 --> 36:13.930
And we've got a world-class coach.

36:18.150 --> 36:19.940
We have to master the 4-4-2 Formation.

36:19.940 --> 36:22.000
That way, we won't panic
and let Yongchuan Hengjiu

36:22.000 --> 36:23.510
throw us off our game.

36:24.880 --> 36:26.250
So where are we going to train?

36:26.250 --> 36:27.280
Where else?

36:27.280 --> 36:28.550
The school field.

36:29.920 --> 36:31.510
We only have two weeks left.

36:31.510 --> 36:33.280
And they have PE classes there every day.

36:33.280 --> 36:34.590
Realistically, we only have

36:34.590 --> 36:35.990
about half a day to train.

36:36.110 --> 36:37.440
Besides, the school closes every day,

36:37.440 --> 36:39.190
so we won't even be able to use the field.

36:39.190 --> 36:40.790
And now with new tactics too,

36:40.880 --> 36:43.610
there's simply no time
to get everything in sync.

36:44.760 --> 36:45.760
That makes sense.

36:46.250 --> 36:48.230
Then, where does Yongchuan Hengjiu

36:48.230 --> 36:49.440
usually train?

36:51.370 --> 36:53.030
This is their training field.

36:54.280 --> 36:55.740
-Oh my god.
-What the hell?

36:56.070 --> 36:57.550
I've never trained at a place

36:57.550 --> 36:58.810
this high-end before.

36:59.440 --> 37:01.230
So what if their field's so fancy?

37:01.230 --> 37:02.840
Doesn't mean a thing if you can't win,

37:02.840 --> 37:03.590
right?

37:03.590 --> 37:04.440
Don't chicken out.

37:04.440 --> 37:05.400
Just go for it.

37:05.400 --> 37:06.070
Yeah.

37:06.070 --> 37:08.360
When have I ever been afraid of anyone?

37:08.880 --> 37:10.150
-You can't defeat me.
-Let me take another look.

37:10.150 --> 37:11.000
Let me see.

37:11.280 --> 37:12.940
Get your spirits up, will you?

37:13.070 --> 37:13.630
Wait.

37:14.280 --> 37:15.210
Are you serious?

37:15.630 --> 37:16.630
As for aerobic endurance,

37:16.630 --> 37:18.710
I think our midfielders are the ones
who need to focus on it.

37:18.710 --> 37:20.000
Zheng Ren, what do you think?

37:20.000 --> 37:21.190
Actually, I think aerobic endurance

37:21.190 --> 37:22.590
helps with

37:22.590 --> 37:23.230
those short bursts

37:23.230 --> 37:24.880
of explosive movement, you know?

37:24.880 --> 37:26.440
And Fu, I think
you should train more on that too.

37:26.440 --> 37:27.070
Yeah, we need to work on it together.

37:27.070 --> 37:27.880
No.

37:27.880 --> 37:28.940
My former manager,

37:29.360 --> 37:30.320
do me a favor.

37:31.550 --> 37:32.190
Zheng Ren!

37:32.190 --> 37:32.590
Pass the ball!

37:32.590 --> 37:34.190
Over here!

37:37.840 --> 37:38.590
Chen Jianghe!

37:38.590 --> 37:39.790
It's okay, it's okay.

37:40.400 --> 37:42.130
Keep moving forward, forward.

37:42.360 --> 37:42.980
Zheng Ren!

37:43.150 --> 37:45.760
You've watched this match footage
over a dozen times already.

37:45.760 --> 37:46.480
Yeah.

37:47.000 --> 37:49.330
The more I watch it,
the more anxious I get.

37:49.870 --> 37:51.310
What should we do?

37:51.360 --> 37:52.630
We don't even have
a proper training facility

37:52.630 --> 37:53.800
for specialized drills.

37:53.800 --> 37:55.190
Are we definitely going to lose?

37:55.190 --> 37:56.320
Don't worry.

37:57.590 --> 37:59.110
I'm their coach.

37:59.110 --> 38:00.320
This is my job.

38:00.880 --> 38:01.800
I'm confiscating

38:01.800 --> 38:03.130
your source of anxiety.

38:07.630 --> 38:08.510
All set.

38:11.760 --> 38:12.280
Come on.

38:13.440 --> 38:14.770
Let's go out for a drink.

38:15.440 --> 38:16.590
A drink?

38:17.190 --> 38:20.230
If you want to drink, why don't we
just make something at your place?

38:20.230 --> 38:21.890
The atmosphere is different.

38:21.920 --> 38:22.920
Going out for a walk

38:22.920 --> 38:24.720
will help you feel less anxious.

38:25.280 --> 38:27.550
I don't want to move.

38:27.550 --> 38:29.110
I'm not in the mood.

38:29.710 --> 38:31.460
If you come with me,

38:31.480 --> 38:32.810
I'll give you a big gift

38:32.880 --> 38:34.540
that you'll definitely love.

38:36.230 --> 38:38.430
Bigger than that PhD application form?

38:38.550 --> 38:40.210
It holds a different meaning.

38:41.360 --> 38:42.110
Fine.

39:03.320 --> 39:05.510
The stars by the sea are so bright.

39:08.230 --> 39:09.480
If you like,

39:09.480 --> 39:10.670
we can come here often.

39:10.670 --> 39:12.400
We can also see stars like these

39:12.880 --> 39:15.610
from the rooftop
where we have tutoring classes.

39:16.440 --> 39:18.320
I think a certain someone

39:18.320 --> 39:19.590
is just lazy.

39:26.760 --> 39:28.190
After building up the suspense
for so long,

39:28.190 --> 39:29.400
you can

39:29.400 --> 39:30.800
bring out the gift for me.

39:33.070 --> 39:33.920
"All set."

39:34.320 --> 39:35.760
I heard your call

39:35.760 --> 39:36.880
with Yu Bo.

39:37.230 --> 39:38.590
When he said "all set,"

39:38.590 --> 39:41.190
did you mean
you've secured a training ground?

39:43.940 --> 39:44.980
I'm wrong?

39:46.480 --> 39:48.550
Then you can call Chairman Wang Genfa

39:48.550 --> 39:49.480
now.

39:50.920 --> 39:53.320
Chairman Wang Genfa is very stingy.

39:53.770 --> 39:55.100
Then I'll make the call.

39:59.400 --> 40:00.510
You guessed right.

40:00.920 --> 40:02.840
I've booked the best training facility
in Hongjing

40:02.840 --> 40:04.640
and a hotel
where the team can stay together.

40:04.640 --> 40:06.570
And I didn't book Hengjiu's place.

40:06.960 --> 40:08.090
I paid for it myself.

40:12.480 --> 40:13.480
No more words.

40:13.510 --> 40:14.630
Let's drink to it.

40:15.280 --> 40:16.150
Cheers.

40:25.050 --> 40:25.860
Are you cold?

40:27.070 --> 40:28.000
A bit.

40:29.490 --> 40:30.410
Come on.

40:49.760 --> 40:50.680
A crab!

40:57.200 --> 40:58.680
Where did it go?

41:15.880 --> 41:17.150
Where did you get it?

41:17.710 --> 41:19.400
They say when fireworks burn,

41:19.400 --> 41:21.200
they create a "wish frequency."

41:21.800 --> 41:24.320
If your heartbeat syncs with it
at that moment,

41:24.320 --> 41:26.380
your wish will definitely come true.

41:28.590 --> 41:30.440
Looks like you've been reading

41:30.440 --> 41:32.770
quite a few psychology books, Coach Wang.

41:36.480 --> 41:37.280
Give it a try?

41:38.000 --> 41:39.460
Let's make a wish together

41:39.670 --> 41:41.070
to win the championship.

41:48.630 --> 41:49.800
You know what?

41:50.360 --> 41:53.930
These sparks are made of magnesium.

41:54.190 --> 41:57.880
Magnesium reacts with carbon dioxide.

41:57.880 --> 42:00.680
So you can't put them out
with a fire extinguisher.

42:02.320 --> 42:05.180
You've switched to
being a chemistry teacher, huh?

42:13.920 --> 42:14.710
Wait.

42:20.840 --> 42:22.150
To put out the fire...

42:26.070 --> 42:28.510
you just need to cover a large area

42:26.890 --> 42:28.790
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

42:29.360 --> 42:31.150
to cut off the carbon dioxide.

42:29.440 --> 42:31.890
♪ On the summer night ♪

42:32.290 --> 42:37.760
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

42:39.310 --> 42:41.720
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

42:42.280 --> 42:48.340
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

42:51.680 --> 42:56.920
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

42:57.530 --> 43:03.210
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

43:03.750 --> 43:04.680
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

43:14.190 --> 43:15.280
-The kids are urging us...
-Let's go.

43:15.280 --> 43:16.340
Let's go find them.

43:22.110 --> 43:23.670
Good evening.

43:24.360 --> 43:25.440
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

43:25.550 --> 43:26.590
Ms. Lin, Coach!

43:26.590 --> 43:27.000
Play football...

43:27.000 --> 43:28.880
-What's wrong?
-I can walk by myself.

43:28.880 --> 43:30.540
-Okay, okay.
-Let me show you.

43:31.510 --> 43:32.770
Ms. Lin is here. Ms. Lin is here.

43:32.770 --> 43:33.760
-Ms. Lin.
-Coach.

43:33.760 --> 43:36.290
-You called us here this late...
-Attention.

43:37.590 --> 43:39.070
Big drinker, tiny tolerance.

43:39.070 --> 43:39.880
She's drunk.

43:42.880 --> 43:44.480
Please sit down, everyone.

43:46.280 --> 43:47.810
Listen to your supervisor.

43:53.390 --> 43:54.850
Sit... Where should I sit?

44:09.840 --> 44:11.280
Do you still remember

44:11.750 --> 44:15.230
how you felt
when you signed this football?

44:16.480 --> 44:17.960
Signed football.

44:17.960 --> 44:19.280
When we make it big,

44:19.280 --> 44:21.000
this'll be priceless.

44:28.480 --> 44:31.740
Now it really feels like a football team
with star players.

44:31.920 --> 44:32.400
Yes.

44:32.400 --> 44:33.280
Technique.

44:34.030 --> 44:34.960
My turn, my turn.

44:36.000 --> 44:38.030
Don't be so quick to forget.

44:39.150 --> 44:40.720
It's for Fu's sake.

44:40.760 --> 44:42.670
I'll just scribble something.

44:44.400 --> 44:45.470
Cool.

44:47.770 --> 44:49.350
Quit pretending, dude.

44:50.480 --> 44:51.110
Here, pen.

44:51.400 --> 44:52.840
So annoying.

45:02.590 --> 45:03.280
Alright, boys.

45:03.280 --> 45:04.030
It's about time.

45:04.030 --> 45:05.560
Hurry up and go to training.

45:06.180 --> 45:08.150
[Feng Suo]

45:15.280 --> 45:17.140
Whoever wasn't serious back then

45:17.550 --> 45:19.320
knows it in their own heart.

45:38.920 --> 45:40.150
Actually,

45:40.630 --> 45:42.630
there's something very important

45:42.630 --> 45:44.070
I still haven't done.

45:54.920 --> 45:59.270
[Feng Suo]

45:59.670 --> 46:01.120
[Lin]

46:05.410 --> 46:06.350
[Lin Wanxing]

46:12.340 --> 46:15.300
Are you willing to sign it now, Mr. Coach?

46:14.330 --> 46:15.640
♪ A starlit night ♪

46:16.220 --> 46:20.740
♪ Secrets falling into my palm ♪

46:21.510 --> 46:22.890
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

46:23.550 --> 46:27.580
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

46:28.170 --> 46:29.580
[Lin Wanxing]

46:28.610 --> 46:29.960
♪ Lasting memories ♪

46:30.720 --> 46:35.040
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

46:35.820 --> 46:36.810
♪ To run toward you ♪

46:37.370 --> 46:41.870
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

46:44.420 --> 46:45.750
[Wang Fa]

46:45.420 --> 46:46.700
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

46:47.890 --> 46:49.220
♪ Because you're with me ♪

46:52.370 --> 46:53.620
♪ The light shimmers ♪

46:55.070 --> 46:56.360
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

46:57.980 --> 46:59.040
♪ Running towards you ♪

46:59.890 --> 47:01.000
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

47:05.040 --> 47:05.950
♪ Walk side by side ♪

47:06.850 --> 47:08.490
♪ Become ourselves ♪

47:10.890 --> 47:11.920
♪ Amid the storm ♪

47:12.660 --> 47:16.940
♪ As our breaths slowly intertwine ♪

47:17.650 --> 47:18.770
♪ Heartbeats alternating ♪
